{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Backrooms Cleanup Crew</strong> is a multiplayer cleaning simulator where you step into the role of a humble cleaner working for F-Corp. You are tasked with cleaning the aftermath of other corporations\u2019 mishaps in the Backrooms. However, nothing is ever that simple in the Backrooms: Clean each room as quickly as possible while avoiding increasingly deadly Incursions.    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/FCorpLobbyGif.gif?t=1739303850\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Team up with up to 3 other players to make quick work of cleaning a variety of levels. Switch between different nozzle types to suit the cleaning at hand. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/BCC_Cleaning128.gif?t=1739303850\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In addition to scrubbing walls, collect and bin all of the objects in the level. Don\u2019t worry about being gentle\u2014feel free to toss items across the room to speed up the process! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/BCC_Binning.gif?t=1739303850\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Beware increasingly difficult and deadly Incursions - dodge between attacks while cleaning any glowing markings to prevent new attacks. Gain power from clearing these markings to make your cleaning even faster. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/BCC_IncursionJump128.gif?t=1739303850\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In addition to the Normal game mode described above, Backrooms Cleanup Crew can be played on Hardcore and Peaceful modes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/BCC_SpookyHouses128.gif?t=1739303850\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Backrooms Cleanup Crew is developed by a two-person team with a love for co-op gaming. We're deeply grateful for your feedback and helping us make this game as fun as possible for you and your crew.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3140990?t=1739303850","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739303850","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/1e11875ac220fc4a8a5d7ad729803bab39db3d32/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739303850","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/1e11875ac220fc4a8a5d7ad729803bab39db3d32/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739303850","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3295910,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Backrooms Cleanup Crew</strong> is a multiplayer cleaning simulator where you step into the role of a humble cleaner working for F-Corp. You are tasked with cleaning the aftermath of other corporations\u2019 mishaps in the Backrooms. However, nothing is ever that simple in the Backrooms: Clean each room as quickly as possible while avoiding increasingly deadly Incursions.    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/FCorpLobbyGif.gif?t=1739303850\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Team up with up to 3 other players to make quick work of cleaning a variety of levels. Switch between different nozzle types to suit the cleaning at hand. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/BCC_Cleaning128.gif?t=1739303850\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In addition to scrubbing walls, collect and bin all of the objects in the level. Don\u2019t worry about being gentle\u2014feel free to toss items across the room to speed up the process! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/BCC_Binning.gif?t=1739303850\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Beware increasingly difficult and deadly Incursions - dodge between attacks while cleaning any glowing markings to prevent new attacks. Gain power from clearing these markings to make your cleaning even faster. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/BCC_IncursionJump128.gif?t=1739303850\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In addition to the Normal game mode described above, Backrooms Cleanup Crew can be played on Hardcore and Peaceful modes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/extras/BCC_SpookyHouses128.gif?t=1739303850\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Backrooms Cleanup Crew is developed by a two-person team with a love for co-op gaming. We're deeply grateful for your feedback and helping us make this game as fun as possible for you and your crew.</p>","developers":["On The Bridge Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140990/header.jpg?t=1739303850","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257091445,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257091445/movie480.mp4?t=1739298333","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257091445/movie_max.mp4?t=1739298333"},"name":"Backrooms Cleanup Crew Official Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257091445/220459fbb0be8302f24ad19058bb56d1f3fa208d/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1739298333","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257091445/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1739298333","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257091445/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1739298333"}}],"name":"Backrooms Cleanup Crew","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10 64-bit or higher<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core i5-4670K / AMD FX-8350 CPU or equivalent<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 8 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 970 / AMD Radeon R9 290 or equivalent<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 5 GB available space</li></ul>"},"platforms":{"linux":false,"mac":false,"windows":true},"publishers":["On The Bridge Games"],"ratings":{"dejus":{"banned":"0","descriptors":"Viol\u00eancia","rating":"12","rating_generated":"1","required_age":"12","use_age_gate":"0"},"steam_germany":{"banned":"0","descriptors":"Gewalt","rating":"16","rating_generated":"1","required_age":"16","use_age_gate":"0"}},"release_date":{"c